        <setting>
            <title>Floating City aka Madame Rouge's Fortress</title>
            <p>The Titans except for Beast Boy and Robotman are in the Devolving Pit. Madame Rouge watches as her soldiers destroy Zandia. She takes pride knowing no country will come save Zandia as its a country where all its citizens are criminals.</p>
