            </charsPresent>
        </setting>
        <setting>
            <title>The New Brotherhood of Evil</title>
            <p>The team is insistent on Beast Boy joining them, but he refuses. Instead, Beast Boy starts to attack. He realizes soonafter that he is very outnumbered and overpowered. Flashback of the destruction of the original Brotherhood of Evil and how the Brain and Mallah survived. Beast Boy decides that it would be beneficial to join the Brotherhood of Evil to stop Madame Rouge and General Zahl.</p>
