        <setting>
            <title>Floating City</title>
            <p>Zandia has fallen. The Titans have all reverted to a primitive state; Robotman is the only one who it didn't work on. Before Madame Rouge can make her next move, Beast Boy and the Brotherhood of Evil show up.</p>
